elements.name: dailyStatementNumber
elements.description: The number assigned to the Daily Statement.

elements.name: dailyStatementPrintDate
elements.description: The date selected in MMDDYY (month, day, year) format for the Daily statement to print.

elements.name: entryFilerCode
elements.description: A unique code assigned by the CBP to all active entry document preparers.

elements.name: filler2
elements.description: Space fill. Reserved filler for possible future expansion of Entry Filer Code

elements.name: importerOfRecordNumber
elements.description: A code representing the importer for whom the Daily statement was prepared (importer statement only).

elements.name: totalEstimatedDuty
elements.description:
A value representing the total duty amount. Two decimal places are implied. If the duty is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

NOTE: Puerto Rican Coffee Duty will be reported within this field for statement generation.

elements.name: totalEstimatedTax
elements.description: A value representing the total tax amount. Two decimal places are implied. If the tax is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: totalDeferredTax
elements.description: A value representing the total deferred tax amount. Two decimal places are implied. If the tax is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: districtPortWhichProcessesEntries
elements.description: A code representing the district/port which processes entries. Valid district/port codes can be queried through the Reference tab of the ACE portal.
